{"tid":199844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯航急瀉　股神單日輸1.8億","createTime":"2017-04-13T13:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T16:02:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19f1f3873bfdcf7145b79fcfa62beb1c51797291","tid":199844,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170413/19989039\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170413%2F19989039&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b22ce3e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170413%2F19989039&h=e03c447e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170413/19989039</a><br />\n<br />\n聯航急瀉　股神單日輸1.8億<br />\n<br />\n34,238<br />\n <br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國聯合航空暴力拖乘客落機事件，拖累航空母企、聯合大陸控股前日股價下跌，連累「股神」畢菲特（圖）賬面蝕2,350萬美元（約1.83億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n去年增持　持股比例9.2%<br />\n畢菲特去年第四季押注美國航空股，分別增持聯合大陸控股、西南航空、達美航空和美國航空。畢菲特增持聯航至2,895萬股，持股比例達9.2%，成聯航最大股東。聯航股價周二收市下跌，單日市值蒸發2.58億美元。假設畢菲特持倉不變，單日賬面輸2,350萬美元；若按聯航前周二全日低位計，畢菲特賬面虧損高達9,150萬美元（約7.14億港元）。<br />\n聯航暴力拖乘客落機事不只拖累「股神」輸錢，或影響公司第二大市場、中國業務表現。據FactSet統計資料，截至去年12月，中國市場佔聯航366億美元全年總收入約6.1%，約22.3億美元，多過競爭對手達美航空。<br />\n■記者伍詠雯  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n挖受害人黑材料　傳媒捱轟<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n網民怒剪聯航卡　莫乃光響應"},{"pid":"eef2836d0dcf00836131c92025d2e85a7ab8e1b8","tid":199844,"uid":61728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"有錢人輸一輸都已經7億幾...仲要對佢黎講係好似冇感覺<br />\n普通人就打工打10世都搵唔到1億"},{"pid":"9481c005141788853fad04d2d01d346beb45dc25","tid":199844,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢人輸一輸都已經7億幾...仲要對佢黎講係好似冇感覺<br />\n普通人就打工打10世都搵唔到1億</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Sgkx46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Sgkx46.jpg&h=48347ad6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ddc72980507cfc2436b39326051df10a8e9d718","tid":199844,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c9d434fed3e80eda3193e41e6dc8ffa4bb58acd","tid":199844,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:42:20.000Z","msg":"我諗好快有人會冇左條命"},{"pid":"cc48d5ca369a1caf47f21996214c3f797a5b76b4","tid":199844,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o27yX9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo27yX9H.png&h=a2b805ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n... 報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}